    <item>
      <title>My shortcode for Code</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-code/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-code/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;This shortcode is useful when you want to display raw code without syntax highlighting or automatic formatting from Hugo. It ensures the output is rendered exactly as written.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Usage&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#usage&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following example shows how to use the shortcode and its rendered output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; code &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;public String toString() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    return null;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; /code &amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;questao-code&#34;&gt;
    &lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-&#34;&gt;
public String toString() {
    return null;
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
    &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>My shortcode for PlantUML</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-plantuml/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-plantuml/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;My shortcode to create diagrams with PlantUML.
This shortcode uses Kroki to render PlantUML diagrams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Example&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#example&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following example shows how to use the shortcode and its rendered output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;{{&amp;lt; plantuml &amp;gt;}}
class Person {
  -id: long
  &amp;#43;getId():long
  &amp;#43;setId(id: long)
}
{{&amp;lt; /plantuml &amp;gt;}}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id=&#34;plantuml-1777228503007652000&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;script&gt;
(async function() {
  const diagram = `\n@startuml\n!theme plain\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam monochrome true\nskinparam classAttributeIconSize 0\nhide stereotype\nhide circle\n\nclass Person \u007b\n  -id: long\n  \u002bgetId():long\n  \u002bsetId(id: long)\n\u007d\n\n@enduml\n`;

  const res = await fetch(&#34;https://kroki.io/plantuml/svg&#34;, {
    method: &#34;POST&#34;,
    headers: { &#34;Content-Type&#34;: &#34;text/plain&#34; },
    body: diagram
  });

  const output = await res.text();
  document.getElementById(&#34;plantuml-1777228503007652000&#34;).innerHTML = output;
})();
&lt;/script&gt;


      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>My shortcode for Questions</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-for-questions/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-for-questions/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;This shortcode is useful for displaying questions with hidden solutions. Question numbers and answer option letters are automatically generated.
This shortcode supports &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-plantuml&#34;&gt;PlantUML&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-code&#34;&gt;code&lt;/a&gt; rendering shortcodes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Usage&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#usage&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following example shows how to use the shortcode and its rendered output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; lista-questoes &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; questao &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;The question description
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; alternativa &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Question alternative
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; /alternativa &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; alternativa &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Question alternative
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; /alternativa &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; solucao letra=&amp;#34;B&amp;#34; &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;The question solution
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; /solucao &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; /questao &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; /lista-questoes &amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;lista-questoes&#34;&gt; 

&lt;div class=&#34;questao-container&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;questao-header&#34;&gt;Questão 1&lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class=&#34;questao-body&#34;&gt; 
The question description 
&lt;li class=&#34;alternativa&#34;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;alternativa-letra&#34;&gt;A.&lt;/span&gt;
     
Question alternative 

&lt;/li&gt;
 
&lt;li class=&#34;alternativa&#34;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;alternativa-letra&#34;&gt;B.&lt;/span&gt;
     
Question alternative 

&lt;/li&gt;
 
&lt;div class=&#34;solucao&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;resposta&#34;&gt;
        
        &lt;div class=&#34;resposta-header&#34;&gt;
            &lt;button
                type=&#34;button&#34;
                onclick=&#34;
                    const body = this.parentElement.nextElementSibling;
                    body.classList.toggle(&#39;hidden&#39;);
                    this.textContent = body.classList.contains(&#39;hidden&#39;)
                        ? &#39;Mostrar solução&#39;
                        : &#39;Ocultar solução&#39;;
                &#34;
            &gt;
                Mostrar solução
            &lt;/button&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;

        
        &lt;div class=&#34;resposta-body hidden&#34;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&#34;resposta-titulo&#34;&gt;
                Resposta correta: &lt;strong&gt;B&lt;/strong&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

             
The question solution 

        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;


      </description>
